{
  "name": "RPlog_Plan_of_Action",
  "title": "Plan of Action",
  "summary": "In a war room aboard a New Republic vessel, Admiral Ackbar convenes a council of officers -- including Vice Admiral Quix, the 224th Battalion captains, and Lightbringer commander Argon Brand -- to plan a first strike against the Imperial fleet blockading Bothawui. Ackbar lays out the intelligence on the Imperial cruisers Responder and Remorseless and proposes punching a small, fast first wave through to Drev'starn to reinforce Lieutenant Halo's beleaguered ground team. Argon argues for an aggressive close jump to preserve surprise and sketches options for committing the heavier MC-40s, while the officer Rasi pushes a decoy scheme using disguised fireship transports to draw and destroy Imperial fire. Ackbar weighs the proposals, endorsing a near jump with a single sacrificial decoy transport to relieve pressure on the convoy as it runs for the spaceport. The council adjourns with the plan taking shape, the session marked to be continued.",
